s2.p:
The following lists the public API changes between the &XercesCName;
           &XercesCVersion; and the &XercesCName; latest code base releases
           of the parser.

ul.li:
Windows application,
shall either change the additional include directories setting, to "..\..\..\..\..\src\xercesc" (Projects->settings->C/C++->Preprocessor). or
change the relevant #include instances, in the source/header files, accordingly, eg
#include <util/XMLString.hpp> be changed to
#include <xercesc/util/XMLString.hpp>
